<font color="#FF0000">BAD DEER IMPOSTER</font><br>
<tt>Sat Oct 25 20:50:08 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
Just field stripped my new obsidian, flint P-38...truely a man's weapon.  Deer hunting trip was not a total failure.. killed two trespassers, three Jehovah's Witnesses, a Navy recruiter and four baby birds.  On the way home, spotted a buck deer lying on the railroad track in front of the Game Warden's house.  I communicated with this rather shabbly buck deer through a secret Lakota sign language.  He revealed that he was protesting deer season.. not because he was afraid that he would be shot..but because he wanted to save the lives of drunken hunters who kept falling out of their deer stands.  I decided to kill him anyway.. but a slow moving train rounded the bend and he jumped up and dashed away.  Darn P-38 doesn't have a long range capability!
<p><code>-- Maybe it was just a goat in disguise  (so sad) </code><p>


